Text: Jeg er i det hele taget forbløffet over denne film har fået negativt kritik. Det fortjerner den ikke, idet filmen skildre skyggesider af dagens unge kvinder med ingredienser af blandt andre trangen for opmærksomhed.

Great job Kefissos! When it comes to quality of the rip I can give both thumbs up. I'm no good on giving a score on that 1-10 scale (like most people do), but hey let me put it this way.. Film looks good on a 40" LCD set. No macro blocks or blurriness whatsoever. The film was also nice. Actually one of the better Danish films I've seen.
